  <summary date="2020-07-31T18:12:56Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Prohibiting Punishment of Acquitted Conduct Act of 2019

This bill limits the consideration of acquitted conduct (e.g., conduct underlying criminal charges for which an individual was found not guilty) by a federal court at sentencing.</summary>
